Hyundai Motor Group Chairman  Chung
Mong Koo  will donate a part of his stake in logistics company
Hyundai Glovis Co. to a local social contribution and cultural
foundation, the group said today in an e-mailed statement. The
shares for donation are worth about 500 billion won ($464
million), it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
